metaData.descriptionCS: The child views a picture and then points to or names the important part missing within a specified time limit.

questions.title: Sample Item. Pencil
questions.correctInstructionsHTML:
Correct response [Lead; Point; Tip of pencil]:

Say, That’s right. The [insert child’s response] is missing.
questions.incorrectInstructionsHTML:
Incorrect response:

Point to the place where the lead is missing and say, You see, the lead is missing.
